If so, you have to write it like this
```{% for item in module.list_items %}
&lt;div class=„something“&gt;
{{ item.email }} 
{{ item.toll_free_number }}
&lt;/div&gt;
{% endfor %}
```

If it’s not a repeater write it like this

```<div class=„something“>
{{ module.list_items.email }} 
{{ module.list_items.toll_free_number }}
</div>```
